reviews.text:
The location is so convenient. Plenty of choices in food as well as choices.
It is near the public transportation. You can spend half day to walk around here. 
For quiet, you can drink coffer and read books here. 
There are high end clothing stores too.
It is also close to schools from child to adulthood.
You can watch movies here too.
You got everything for medium price shopping here.  Surrounded by residential. commerical building and therefore always packed

A good, rather relaxed mall in the Kwun Tong area which is focused mostly on everyday items rather than luxury goods. Spread out over a larger area rather than several floors, the mall is quick to get around. Has several restaurants and good connections thanks to the MTR right next to it.
Well rounded MTR mall with plenty of shops and restaurants.
Nice mall, just near MTR station.
